videoSnippet.title: So Many Snacks, So Little Time! | Jones vs Gukesh D | Isle of Man (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Gewain Jones vs Gukesh D
Isle of Man Open Tournament, Round 4
24 Oct 2018.
Slav Defense: Exchange Variation (D10)

1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. cxd5 cxd5 4. Bg5 h6 5. Bh4 Qb6 6. Nc3 Qxb2 7. Nxd5 e6 8. Rb1 Qa3 9. Qc2 Na6 10. e4 Bd6 11. Bb5+ Kf8 12. Nc3 Nb4 13. Qd2 a6 14. Be2 g5 15. Bg3 Bxg3 16. hxg3 Nc6 17. Nf3 Qd6 18. d5 exd5 19. Nxd5 Nge7 20. Nxg5 Qg6 21. Nb6 Rb8 22. Rh4 Qg7 23. Nxf7 Kxf7 24. Rf4+ Ke8 25. Bh5+ Ng6 26. Qd6 Rg8 27. Bxg6+ Qxg6 28. Rf8+
